name: Fiberglass Cream Hardener
short_description: Designed to be used with body fillers, bondo-glass, bondo-hair and fiberglass resin jelly. Specially formulated and packaged under temperature controlled conditions that assure freshness and maximum performance. The red color cream hardener provides a color change when mixed with Bondo Filler or other white auto body fillers. On a card.

name: 1 Quart Body Filler
short_description: Shapes in minutes and is formulated to be a non-shrinking, non-reactive and permanently durable material for repairing metal, wood, steel and plastic. Repairs dents, patches holes and leaks and restores chips quickly and easily. Complete autobody projects the same day started. Includes cream hardener.

name: Plastic Spreaders
meta_description: For smooth, easy spreading of all Bondo products.
description: For smooth, easy spreading of all Bondo products.
